<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HMS About</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/HMSAbout.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css"> <!-- AOS Library -->
    <style>
        /* Basic styling for the layout */
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f4f6f9, #dbe6f6);
            color: #333;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: relative;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out; /* Add fade-in animation */
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: "";
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            bottom: -8px;
        }

        .gallery {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .gallery img {
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            border: 4px solid #3498db;
        }

        .gallery img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1); /* Add a hover zoom effect */
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* Counter Section */
        .stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .stats .stat-item {
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        .stat-item h2 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #27ae60;
        }

        .stat-item p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Keyframe Animations */
        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @@keyframes fadeInUp {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Hospital Overview -->
        <div class="section" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h1 class="section-title">Welcome to Our Hospital</h1>
            <p>
                Our hospital is dedicated to providing top-quality healthcare services to the community. With advanced facilities and a dedicated team, we strive to ensure the best care for our patients.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Counter Section -->
        <div class="stats" data-aos="zoom-in">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <h2>200+</h2>
                <p>Doctors</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <h2>5000+</h2>
                <p>Patients Treated</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <h2>10+</h2>
                <p>Departments</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Photo Gallery -->
        <div class="section" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="section-title">Gallery of Our Facilities</h2>
            <div class="gallery">
                <img src="~/images/1 (1).jpg" alt="Reception Area">
                <img src="~/images/1 (2).jpg" alt="Patient Room">
                <img src="~/images/1 (3).jpg" alt="Emergency Room">
                <img src="~/images/1 (4).jpg" alt="Operating Theater">
                <img src="~/images/1 (5).jpg" alt="Laboratory">
                <img src="~/images/1 (6).jpg" alt="Outdoor View">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Departments and Services -->
        <div class="section" data-aos="fade-right">
            <h2 class="section-title">Departments and Services</h2>
            <p>We offer a range of specialized services, including Cardiology, Pediatrics, Radiology, and more. Our state-of-the-art equipment ensures that patients receive the best possible care.</p>
            <a href="#services" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Meet Our Team -->
        <div class="section" data-aos="fade-left">
            <h2 class="section-title">Meet Our Team</h2>
            <p>Our dedicated team of doctors, nurses, and staff work tirelessly to ensure the health and well-being of our patients. We take pride in our compassionate care and commitment to excellence.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Achievements -->
        <div class="section" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="section-title">Achievements and Awards</h2>
            <p>We are proud of our achievements in healthcare excellence. Our hospital has received numerous awards for outstanding patient care and innovation in medical practices.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AOS Library -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init();
    </script>
</body>

</html>
